        Lots of stencils all reflexive with various dimensions..
    /Volumes/unified-model/trunk/src/atmosphere/UKCA/ukca_fastjx.F90:
        Reflexive stencils both with ranges and with explicit induction vars.
    /Volumes/unified-model/trunk/src/atmosphere/UKCA/ukca_mode_ems_um_mod.F90:
